Easy hosting backup

Features :
- Easy instalation/configuration
- Backup a folder and a DB in a single tar.gz file
- Keep daily, weekly, monthly backups
- Configure how many of backups to keep

Install :
- Copy files in a private folder on you webserver
- Edit backup.cfp to suit your needs
- Setup a daily cron job to launch backup.sh
- Relax...

Tested on :
- Vps.net
- Rackspace CloudSites
- Ubuntu 11.10

